01:13:17,392 --> 01:13:18,120
Netřeba.

1021
01:13:19,861 --> 01:13:20,691
Mitsuki!

1022
01:13:21,896 --> 01:13:22,728
Jsi v pořádku?

1023
01:13:22,997 --> 01:13:24,396
